data.description: Situated within the serene confines of Mountain Home, this parcel of land promises a peaceful and private lifestyle.  Ideal for a family residence, with minimal restrictions.  This land is perfect for watching the wildlife, listening to the birds, and perfect for star gazing. So, get away from it all and move to the country! Property will need a well and septic.
